product.name: Fresh Littleneck Clams
product.description: Fresh Littleneck Clams, Live-in-shell, wild harvest, product of Canada or U.S.A., sold in one pound increments.  Approx 10-12 clams per pound.

product.name: Fogo Island Cod
product.description: Sustainably caught in a small artisanal fishery off the coast of Fogo Island, Newfoundland.  Wild-caught, skin-on, Atlantic cod. Product of Canada. Sold per pound, portions are cut in varying sizes.  Typically 1-3 portions per pound.
